{
  "stem": "23645.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although the Jews in France didn't fare that well during the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Were there any early warning signs before the war?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, anti-Semitism was-- was everywhere, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, in 1938-- when I get back to 1938 and '39, before the war broke out-- we-- there were German Jews that were coming.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, after Kristallnacht, there were-- some of them were coming into Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, they was-- they were telling us what-- what was about to happen and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was this talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so did-- some of the-- the neighbors, as I told you before, they would come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we would gather for all the happy occasions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They also came to our house because my father was quite good at giving advice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they came for him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was sort of looked up-- excuse me-- in the community.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they would come to Chil Waisman for advice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would come to him to talk things over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I remember when they would come and express their fears.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They says, did you hear about what's happening in, in, in Germany?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if, if the war breaks out, and they win, and they come into Poland, they want to kill Jews, left and right!",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember so distinctly my father, you know, saying, you crazy?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they have-- look at that-- they have Beethoven, they have Schubert, they have-- at that time, he was mentioning Schuler, you know, because he liked to read a lot.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, Schuler and Heine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh-- all these poets and these composers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- he says, Germany, they're so advanced of all the-- of all of Europe, of all the world, he was saying.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What are you worried about?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
